name: Create Timing time entries from Google Sheets spreadsheet rows
description: Make will watch for new rows in a specified Google Sheets spreadsheet at regular intervals and create a time entry in Timing using information received. The template uses this [example spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1qgLbjEfROsnledj6q-TdmOdAdl1idzU6s7c008wKhws/edit?usp=sharing).
